text: Dino De Antoni (12 July 1936 - 22 March 2019) was an Italian Roman Catholic archbishop. De Antoni was born in Italy and was ordained to the priesthood in 1960. He served as archbishop of the Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Gorizia, Italy from 1999 to 2012.Dino De Antoni ==Notes== Category:1936 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Italian Roman Catholic archbishops
